Slow down.

257
00:21:53,400 --> 00:21:56,400
I'm all right. Go ahead.

258
00:21:59,300 --> 00:22:01,200
I'll tell you when you finish eating.

259
00:22:01,200 --> 00:22:03,000
Okay.

260
00:22:04,800 --> 00:22:07,400
Senior, I searched online.

261
00:22:07,400 --> 00:22:11,200
The train from Edinburgh to Birmingham takes four hours.

262
00:22:11,200 --> 00:22:14,500
How often do you think we should meet up?

263
00:22:16,000 --> 00:22:19,330
I say we should meet every two weeks.

264
00:22:19,330 --> 00:22:21,500
If we're really busy, then we should meet at least once a month.

265
00:22:21,500 --> 00:22:25,100
A month is the longest I can endure.

266
00:22:35,200 --> 00:22:40,400
What happens if we're so busy that we can't meet up?

267
00:22:40,400 --> 00:22:45,800
That's okay. Even if we're busy, I'll still find a way to see you.

268
00:22:47,200 --> 00:22:51,600
- I never knew that our Miaomiao has already thought things through.
- Right.

269
00:22:52,600 --> 00:22:55,400
What happens if... for some reasons I can't leave the country?

270
00:22:55,400 --> 00:22:58,450
What happens if... for some reasons I can't leave the country?

271
00:23:01,200 --> 00:23:04,800
Then, I'll wait for when you're able to leave the country.

272
00:23:04,800 --> 00:23:07,000
There should be a postponement period for exchange students.

273
00:23:07,000 --> 00:23:12,200
If you can't, then I can register for a postgraduate in Birmingham University.

274
00:23:12,200 --> 00:23:15,800
Anyway, we will be able to leave together.

275
00:23:36,200 --> 00:23:41,700
What you just said wasn't for real, right?

276
00:23:43,200 --> 00:23:47,580
No, it wasn't. I was just thinking.

277
00:23:48,200 --> 00:23:52,000
But you said that you have something to tell me.

278
00:23:53,400 --> 00:23:55,000
Yes, I do.

279
00:23:58,400 --> 00:24:01,600
I was saying that when the theme park closes,

280
00:24:01,600 --> 00:24:04,400
we'll go and ride the ferris wheel.

281
00:24:06,200 --> 00:24:08,700
Won't we get caught?

282
00:24:08,700 --> 00:24:11,100
You believed that?

283
00:24:11,100 --> 00:24:15,100
Do you think that teasing me is fun?

284
00:24:15,100 --> 00:24:17,300
It's pretty fun.

285
00:24:24,800 --> 00:24:32,000
But... really... I have something that I would like to tell you.

286
00:24:32,800 --> 00:24:34,800
What's wrong?

287
00:24:37,400 --> 00:24:40,400
When you took me home yesterday,

288
00:24:40,400 --> 00:24:44,300
I said "Thank you for buying me drinks".

289
00:24:44,300 --> 00:24:47,300
But what I really wanted to say was,

290
00:24:47,300 --> 00:24:53,200
"Thanks that you gave me the motivation to apply to Birmingham."

291
00:24:53,200 --> 00:24:59,000
Without you, I wouldn't have even dreamt of going to Birmingham.

292
00:25:01,210 --> 00:25:05,950
So I want to say, thank you.

293
00:26:04,800 --> 00:26:05,700
Miaomiao.

294
00:26:05,700 --> 00:26:09,300
Can you please not tell me anything now.

295
00:26:46,400 --> 00:26:47,950
There's so much medicine.

296
00:26:47,950 --> 00:26:50,900
What had you been doing recently? A side business?

297
00:26:50,900 --> 00:26:53,700
It's nothing to do with you. Go and play your games.

298
00:27:17,700 --> 00:27:22,000
Liang Younian

299
00:27:27,500 --> 00:27:29,800
Teacher Li, is there anything wrong?

300
00:27:29,800 --> 00:27:32,800
Kaituo, can you come to the model classroom?

301
00:27:32,800 --> 00:27:34,400
Okay.

302
00:27:38,000 --> 00:27:40,000
Bye.

303
00:27:53,600 --> 00:27:56,900
- Teacher Li.
- Teacher Jia.

304
00:27:56,900 --> 00:27:59,600
I just went to your office only to find that no one was present.

305
00:27:59,600 --> 00:28:01,800
Teacher Jia, is there anything that you need?

306
00:28:01,800 --> 00:28:03,920
I was coming to get Xia Miaomiao's first-year grades.

307
00:28:03,920 --> 00:28:06,800
I need them for the "Change of Department" test.

308
00:28:06,800 --> 00:28:09,210
Okay, okay. Can you wait a minute?

309
00:28:09,210 --> 00:28:10,800
I just finished class and I need to tidy up.

310
00:28:10,800 --> 00:28:12,800
- Please wait a minute.
- Okay.

311
00:28:14,400 --> 00:28:16,400
Are you free to eat lunch together today?

312
00:28:16,400 --> 00:28:17,800
It's okay, I've already eaten.

313
00:28:17,800 --> 00:28:20,380
Can you hurry up? I'm quite busy.

314
00:28:27,500 --> 00:28:29,890
I've just come back to Haicheng from abroad.

315
00:28:29,890 --> 00:28:32,400
Do you have time to eat tonight?

316
00:28:32,400 --> 00:28:36,200
I know... I know, I'll come home and eat.

317
00:28:37,000 --> 00:28:38,900
My mom is so annoying.

318
00:28:38,900 --> 00:28:40,600
Are you done? If you're done, can we get going?

319
00:28:40,600 --> 00:28:43,560
Teacher. Jia, I have something to say to you.

320
00:28:43,560 --> 00:28:44,800
Lu Peng told me—

321
00:28:44,800 --> 00:28:48,000
I... I have no interest in your family matters. Hurry up and go.

322
00:28:48,000 --> 00:28:50,600
Do you know that I like you?

323
00:28:55,740 --> 00:28:59,350
- That—
-There's no need to say anything. I know what you're going to say.

324
00:28:59,400 --> 00:29:02,000
First, listen to what I have to say.

325
00:29:02,900 --> 00:29:06,500
I've always quite liked you.

326
00:29:06,500 --> 00:29:11,000
I've noticed that you've been avoiding me recently.

327
00:29:11,000 --> 00:29:14,800
I may not be your ideal type,

328
00:29:14,800 --> 00:29:17,400
but I've been trying very hard to change myself.

329
00:29:17,400 --> 00:29:21,800
I would like you to give me a chance, okay?

330
00:29:24,700 --> 00:29:26,900
- Teacher Li.
- Teacher Li.

331
00:29:26,900 --> 00:29:27,960
Oh, look, there's a student looking for you.

332
00:29:27,960 --> 00:29:31,200
Can you get someone to deliver Miaomiao's grades to me another day.

333
00:29:31,200 --> 00:29:33,200
Thanks!

334
00:29:36,180 --> 00:29:39,010
What happened with TeacherJia? Why is she running so fast?

335
00:29:42,400 --> 00:29:46,200
Nothing, it's not important.

336
00:29:46,200 --> 00:29:50,100
Oh, yes. Can you please persuade Liang Younian.

337
00:29:50,100 --> 00:29:52,100
I don't know what to do about him.

338
00:29:52,100 --> 00:29:54,900
I'm this close to giving Senior Liang Gang a call.

339
00:29:54,900 --> 00:29:56,700
What's wrong?

340
00:29:56,700 --> 00:29:59,200
He is giving up his opportunity to go abroad.

341
00:30:00,200 --> 00:30:01,400
Why?

342
00:30:01,400 --> 00:30:06,500
I also don't know why. He isn't telling me.

343
00:30:09,600 --> 00:30:12,000
Okay, then I'll find time to ask him about it.

344
00:30:12,000 --> 00:30:15,200
Don't find time. Do it now.

345
00:30:16,000 --> 00:30:17,500
Okay.

346
00:30:24,400 --> 00:30:28,200
I understand. Let's talk later.

347
00:30:28,200 --> 00:30:30,800
So why are you giving up this opportunity?

348
00:30:33,600 --> 00:30:34,980
It's inconvenient right now.

349
00:30:34,980 --> 00:30:37,100
I'll tell you when I get back.

350
00:30:37,800 --> 00:30:39,910
Senior, what are you doing?

351
00:30:39,910 --> 00:30:42,400
I've been looking all over for you.

352
00:30:44,970 --> 00:30:47,000
Why are you buying so much?

353
00:30:47,000 --> 00:30:48,420
I searched online.

354
00:30:48,420 --> 00:30:51,000
Lots of people buy these things when they leave China.

355
00:30:51,900 --> 00:30:54,400
You can buy these abroad, too.

356
00:30:54,400 --> 00:30:57,100
But it's more expensive abroad.

357
00:30:58,000 --> 00:30:59,460
But this is too much.

358
00:30:59,460 --> 00:31:02,000
It'll be too heavy to take on the plane.

359
00:31:02,000 --> 00:31:05,000
I can carry it all myself. I can.

360
00:31:05,000 --> 00:31:08,680
There's so much and I won't even be there.

361
00:31:08,680 --> 00:31:09,800
How can you carry all of these?

362
00:31:09,800 --> 00:31:10,980
Be good, let's put it all back.

363
00:31:10,980 --> 00:31:12,600
We can buy it when we're abroad.

364
00:31:12,600 --> 00:31:16,000
I said I can carry it all myself.

365
00:31:17,000 --> 00:31:20,100
One bag, no more than that.

366
00:31:20,100 --> 00:31:21,900
Five bags.

367
00:31:22,800 --> 00:31:24,200
- Two bags.
- Four bags.

368
00:31:24,200 --> 00:31:27,800
- Okay, then let's just take one bag.
-Okay, okay, let's take two bags.

369
00:31:38,600 --> 00:31:41,600
Will you not even let me take one jar of Lao Gan Ma?
 (Popular Chinese hot sauce)

370
00:31:44,000 --> 00:31:44,900
No.

371
00:31:44,900 --> 00:31:47,900
Th-Then I'll bring the hotpot sauce, right?

372
00:31:47,900 --> 00:31:51,000
- Only one packet.
- How about two packets?

373
00:31:51,800 --> 00:31:53,800
Xia Miaomiao.

374
00:31:56,400 --> 00:31:59,600
Okay, have it your way. I won't bring any.

375
00:32:01,400 --> 00:32:02,800
Let's have a look at what else there is.

376
00:32:02,800 --> 00:32:05,200
Even if we look, you still would not let me buy it.

377
00:32:39,400 --> 00:32:41,700
Thank you, thank you.

378
00:32:57,200 --> 00:32:59,200
Hello, Uncle.

379
00:33:10,600 --> 00:33:12,400
Then let's get straight to the point.

380
00:33:12,400 --> 00:33:14,400
What do you want to do?

381
00:33:16,970 --> 00:33:19,850
You know that I'm unsatisfied with you, right?

382
00:33:22,660 --> 00:33:25,550
I know you have an ulterior motive in approaching Xiaoyue.

383
00:33:25,550 --> 00:33:28,430
However, there's nothing I can do since she likes you.

384
00:33:29,300 --> 00:33:32,930
So what else is it that you're not pleased about?

385
00:33:32,930 --> 00:33:35,030
Hold on, Sir. You might be—

386
00:33:35,030 --> 00:33:37,330
All right, you can leave now.

387
00:33:37,330 --> 00:33:39,350
Anyway, bear this in mind.

388
00:33:39,350 --> 00:33:41,630
I will be watching you.

389
00:33:41,630 --> 00:33:43,570
You better be careful.

390
00:33:50,150 --> 00:33:53,430
Sir, then I'll get going.

391
00:34:23,600 --> 00:34:24,740
How come you're here?

392
00:34:24,740 --> 00:34:27,510
Don't you know why I am here?

393
00:34:29,470 --> 00:34:32,030
Where are all my roommates?

394
00:34:32,030 --> 00:34:33,540
They are having dinner.

395
00:34:33,540 --> 00:34:37,300
So can you tell me now, why aren't you going to study abroad?

396
00:34:40,740 --> 00:34:42,470
They're all having dinner?

397
00:34:42,470 --> 00:34:44,160
Have you had dinner yet?

398
00:34:44,940 --> 00:34:47,200
Liang Younian, don't change the subject.

399
00:34:47,200 --> 00:34:49,920
You must answer me now.

400
00:34:55,140 --> 00:34:56,590
My phone is ringing.

401
00:34:56,590 --> 00:34:59,230
Don't answer it. Answer my question first.

402
00:35:01,250 --> 00:35:04,390
It's He Xin, should I answer it?

403
00:35:09,260 --> 00:35:12,560
Answer... She's in such a remote place.

404
00:35:12,560 --> 00:35:15,790
What if there's an accident? Right?

405
00:35:23,550 --> 00:35:28,230
Liang Younian! Can you stop sending me random things?

406
00:35:29,120 --> 00:35:30,950
I live in the mountains.

407
00:35:30,950 --> 00:35:35,730
Why did you send me candied sweet potatoes and honey?

408
00:35:35,730 --> 00:35:37,540
When did I—

409
00:35:40,070 --> 00:35:43,170
I have to walk a couple of kilometers to pick up a parcel.

410
00:35:43,170 --> 00:35:46,780
Can I not buy agricultural products from the farmers here?

411
00:35:46,780 --> 00:35:50,510
Are you pulling a prank on me, or are you that stupid?

412
00:35:51,630 --> 00:35:53,660
All right, Xinxin.

413
00:35:54,750 --> 00:35:59,950
Then next time, I'll send you some things that make more sense?

414
00:36:01,850 --> 00:36:04,740
Wang Yichao is calling me, so I'll hang up first.

415
00:36:04,740 --> 00:36:06,670
Hey—

416
00:36:17,700 --> 00:36:18,900
Ask Lin Kaituo to come along.

417
00:36:18,900 --> 00:36:21,380
Meet me in your model classroom.

418
00:36:40,460 --> 00:36:43,300
What is this? Are you selling beer?

419
00:36:44,350 --> 00:36:45,660
Don't bring it up.

420
00:36:45,660 --> 00:36:48,860
Xiaoyue's dad reprimanded me today.

421
00:36:51,780 --> 00:36:54,100
Her dad really had the guts.

422
00:36:54,100 --> 00:36:55,920
He dares to bully our Da Chao.

423
00:36:55,920 --> 00:36:59,020
Don't get mad. What did he say?

424
00:37:02,870 --> 00:37:08,310
Simply put, he thinks that I'm an ordinary citizen.

425
00:37:08,350 --> 00:37:10,770
Their family is way out of my league.

426
00:37:10,770 --> 00:37:12,470
It's really nothing.

427
00:37:12,470 --> 00:37:14,530
I just haven't been looked down by someone in a long time.

428
00:37:14,530 --> 00:37:16,590
I'm just not used to it.

429
00:37:18,830 --> 00:37:20,760
It's fine when you get used to it.

430
00:37:20,760 --> 00:37:23,880
He Xin just called me "stupid".

431
00:37:27,180 --> 00:37:29,490
We really are birds of the same feather.

432
00:37:35,680 --> 00:37:39,460
It seems that only our Younian is doing well.

433
00:37:40,320 --> 00:37:42,320
Miaomiao is obedient and mature.

434
00:37:42,320 --> 00:37:44,920
Her dad is often out at sea.

435
00:37:44,920 --> 00:37:48,390
He 's going abroad with her soon.

436
00:37:48,460 --> 00:37:50,940
They are the perfect couple.

437
00:37:53,380 --> 00:37:55,580
He's not going abroad anymore.

438
00:37:56,720 --> 00:37:59,950
What? Why?

439
00:38:12,470 --> 00:38:15,530
My mom's unfinished project has been restarted.

440
00:38:15,530 --> 00:38:17,780
I intend to take part in it.

441
00:38:19,400 --> 00:38:21,630
Then what about Xia Miaomiao?

442
00:38:22,430 --> 00:38:23,790
I haven't told her yet.

443
00:38:23,790 --> 00:38:26,990
I'm afraid she won't study abroad if she finds out.

444
00:38:30,700 --> 00:38:32,220
You can't do this.

445
00:38:32,220 --> 00:38:33,590
You have to make it clear to her.

446
00:38:33,590 --> 00:38:35,230
She will empathize with you.

447
00:38:43,790 --> 00:38:46,240
I wanted to tell her.

448
00:38:46,240 --> 00:38:49,510
But she said she would wait until we could go together.

449
00:38:50,600 --> 00:38:54,300
I don't know when this project will be done.

450
00:38:57,140 --> 00:39:01,050
I think that her plans shouldn't be messed up because of me.

451
00:39:01,800 --> 00:39:05,350
She should do what she wants to do.

452
00:39:37,230 --> 00:39:39,280
Lin Kaituo told me to come and pick you up.

453
00:39:39,280 --> 00:39:43,020
Senior, why did you drink so much beer?

454
00:39:46,320 --> 00:39:48,420
Yes!

