00:40:55,760 --> 00:40:59,830
You're sorry? Sorry for what?

462
00:41:11,060 --> 00:41:14,400
I'm sorry I took your pickles.

463
00:41:21,580 --> 00:41:26,180
Who is it? Who broke the lock for the swimming pool?

464
00:41:27,110 --> 00:41:29,100
Who is it?

465
00:41:36,920 --> 00:41:40,740
You young people can date anywhere.

466
00:41:40,740 --> 00:41:41,800
The campus is huge.

467
00:41:41,800 --> 00:41:43,750
